originalText.text: I have always had such a positive experience at this urgent care center. Most of my experience with them has been covid testing in the 2020 - 2022 years, but I have come in for other reasons as well and always felt that they were courteous, quick (even when very busy) and provided great care. I'm happy to have them around the corner.

originalText.text: I've gotten probably 15 COVID tests here over the course of the pandemic, and I could not recommend them more highly. The staff is kind, the service is ridiculously quick (especially relative to some other spots I've tried), and it's such a low-hassle, easy experience all around. I've never made an appointment in advance and have also never needed to wait more than 10 minutes at a time. (I steer clear of the immediate post-work rush, but I've gone at lots of different time of day and always found it completely manageable.) Huge, huge fan.

originalText.text: I had such an amazing experience at Statcare Urgent & walk-in Medical care!! They were so quick to check me in and get me into a room within minutes of arriving. Our physician Amy was so pleasant and listened to all my needs and questions. She made visiting the clinic very comfortable and she gave such exceptional service!

originalText.text: Best urgent care experience I've ever had. Walked in around 2pm, gave info, and got called back within a couple of minutes. From the reception staff, to our nurse, Dr, and check out staff, everyone was so helpful, professional, and fast. My daughter had the stomach flu and was able to get meds and a note to excuse her absence from college classes within 15+/- minutes. With her insurance,  copay was $20. Very satisfied with experience.
